divs: sighting detailsat home taking pictures of sky\clouds near sunset--facing south west. unsure of shape\size of object until i was able to view it enlarged on my pc. object appears to be a domed saucer shape when slightly enlarged. the left side is either entering or exiting the cloud. a second picture was taken directly after without zooming in on the cloud-which also gives a better perspective of the distance. both pictures were taken within a few seconds of each other. nothing appears to be in the 2nd photo. unsure of direction of object.
Summary: Captured unknown object on digital camera while taking photos of sky/clouds near sunset.
trends: There have been no other sightings in New Galilee
This sighting has never been favorited.
